{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Plan: 1. Update Compose and container assets for `frontend`, `backend`, `postgres`, and a file-backed `gcs` emulator, keeping the existing browser QA container intact if it still fits. 2. Add the minimal backend config surface needed for...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_28", "text": "Plan:\n1. Update Compose and container assets for `frontend`, `backend`, `postgres`, and a file-backed `gcs` emulator, keeping the existing browser QA container intact if it still fits.\n2. Add the minimal backend config surface needed for database and storage env wiring so the stack is self-describing instead of Compose-only knowledge.\n3. Update README and infra docs with safe startup, shutdown, and data-reset guidance for the persistent volumes.\n4. Verify with config checks, targeted tests, and an actual Compose bring-up/health pass before writing the required task summary.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 57, "prompt_index": 5, "prompt_name": "04 \u2014 Docker Compose Foundation", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-03-31T21:32:13-07:00"}
